<h2 id="c">C</h2>

<h3 id="contextual-image-classification">Contextual image classification</h3>
<p>A topic of pattern recognition in computer vision, is an approach of classification based on contextual information in 
images. ‚ÄúContextual‚Äù means this approach is focusing on the relationship of the nearby pixels, which is also called 
the neighbourhood.</p>

<h3 id="cryogen">Cryogen</h3>
<p>A substance used to produce low temperatures; a freezing mixture. Examples are liquid nitrogen and dry ice.</p>

