<h2 id="h">H</h2>

<h3 id="hyperspectral-imaging">Hyperspectral Imaging</h3>
<p>Hyperspectral imaging, like other spectral imaging, collects and processes information from across the electromagnetic 
spectrum. The goal of hyperspectral imaging is to obtain the spectrum for each pixel in the image of a scene, with the 
purpose of finding objects, identifying materials, or detecting processes.</p>

